@startuml scan_flow
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
'  ACR-QA  v4.0.0  —  End-to-End Scan Flow  (A4-portrait edition)
'  5 participants — fits portrait A4 text width
'  King Salman International University  ·  CSE494  ·  2025-26
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor   #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName   "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize   10
skinparam shadowing         false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize    160
skinparam wrapWidth         160

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor     #002654
  BorderThickness 2
  FontSize        10
}
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #DBEAFE
  BorderColor     #002654
  BorderThickness 2
  FontSize        10
}
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor              #002654
  ArrowFontColor          #374151
  ArrowFontSize           9
  ArrowThickness          1.5
  DividerBackgroundColor  #F3F4F6
  DividerBorderColor      #9CA3AF
  DividerFontColor        #111827
  DividerFontSize         10
  DividerFontStyle        bold
  GroupBackgroundColor    #F9FAFB
  GroupBorderColor        #D1D5DB
  GroupBorderThickness    1.5
  NoteBackgroundColor     #FFFDE7
  NoteBorderColor         #C9A84C
  NoteFontSize            9
  LifeLineBorderColor     #9CA3AF
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
}


'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  5 PARTICIPANTS  (slim enough for A4 portrait)
'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
actor       "Developer\n/ CI/CD"              as DEV
participant "FastAPI\n:8000"                  as API   #BBF7D0
participant "Celery Worker\n+ Redis broker"   as WRK   #E0F2FE
participant "CORE Pipeline\n(14 engines)"     as CORE  #FDE68A
database    "PostgreSQL 15"                   as DB    #FED7AA


'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  PHASE 1 — TRIGGER
'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Phase 1  ·  Trigger & Job Creation ==

DEV  ->  API  : POST /v1/scan {repo_url, branch}\nor GitHub webhook / CI badge
activate API

API  ->  API  : JWT / API-Key auth\nRedis rate-limit check
API  ->  DB   : INSERT analysis_runs {status=QUEUED}
activate DB
DB   --> API  : run_id
deactivate DB

API  ->  WRK  : enqueue scan_repository.delay(run_id)
activate WRK
API  --> DEV  : HTTP 202 Accepted {run_id}
deactivate API


'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  PHASE 2 — ASYNC PIPELINE EXECUTION
'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Phase 2  ·  Async Pipeline (Celery) ==

WRK  ->  DB   : UPDATE run SET status=RUNNING
WRK  ->  CORE : run_pipeline(run_id, repo_path)
activate CORE

note over CORE
  Stage 2: 12+ tools in parallel thread pool
  Ruff · Bandit · Semgrep · ESLint · gosec
  Vulture · Radon · jscpd · npm audit ...
end note

CORE ->  CORE : Stage 3: normalise → CanonicalFinding\ntaint_analyse · reachability_bfs\ndedup (−33% noise) · confidence_score

CORE ->  CORE : Stage 4 RAG: dict_lookup O(1)\nGroq LLaMA-3.3-70B × 3 runs\nentropy_filter τ=3.2 bits

note right of CORE
  97.1% overall precision
  100% security-class precision
  100% AI enrichment rate
end note

CORE ->  CORE : Stage 5: SCA + CBoM (62 algos)\nStage 6: quality_gate(.acrqa.yml)\nStage 7: Dilithium3 attestation


'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  PHASE 3 — PERSIST & DELIVER
'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Phase 3  ·  Persist & Deliver ==

CORE --> WRK  : pipeline complete
deactivate CORE

WRK  ->  DB   : INSERT findings · llm_explanations\nINSERT attestations · sbom_records\nUPDATE run SET status=COMPLETED
activate DB
DB   --> WRK  : committed
deactivate DB
deactivate WRK

DEV  ->  API  : GET /v1/runs/{run_id}/findings
activate API
API  ->  DB   : SELECT findings + enrichment
activate DB
DB   --> API  : findings[]
deactivate DB
API  --> DEV  : JSON / SARIF / Markdown
deactivate API


'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  PHASE 4 — FEEDBACK LOOP
'════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Phase 4  ·  Developer Feedback ==

DEV  ->  API  : POST /v1/feedback {finding_id, verdict: TP|FP}
activate API
API  ->  DB   : UPDATE suppression_rules · adjust threshold
deactivate API

note over DEV, DB
  Typical end-to-end: 14–90 s
  Tool execution: ~10 s · Taint+Reachability: <1 s
  AI enrichment: 400–1400 ms per finding
  Load tested: 500 RPS · p99 < 2 s (non-AI endpoints)
end note

@enduml
